Package eu.advance.logistics.flow.engine.model.fd Description

The flow-description record classes and exceptions thrown when parsing a flow XML.

To parse a flow XML conforming the schemas/flow-description.xsd, use the 


 AdvanceCompositeBlock.parseFlow(XElement.parseXML("flow.xml"));

To serialize a flow, call the serializeFlow() instance method on a composite block.
